&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;According to the question:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Now,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Given equation: 9 &amp;times; 2 &amp;minus; (150 &amp;divide; 5) + 24 + (32 &amp;divide; 8) &amp;times; 6 + 15 = 71&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;1) Interchange 6 and 5&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

